{"tid":778423,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"自成一角－Sony 正式命名自家 Marvel 電影宇宙觀","createTime":"2018-08-13T16:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T09:39:25.000Z","uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"526512023bacc9549f0f71fdaae1569206aeffb5","tid":778423,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:25:27.000Z","msg":"<strong>自成一角－Sony 正式命名自家 Marvel 電影宇宙觀<br />\n除了蜘蛛俠外其實還有 900 個潛在角色可供使用。</strong><br />\n<br />\n編輯 : Sai<br />\n/<br />\n7 小時前<br />\n/<br />\nEntertainment 娛樂<br />\n早前隨着釋出《Venom》最新電影預告片，我們 HYPEBEAST 亦順勢剖析預告當中內容，因為電影將重點揭示共生體家族，逐步發展更多成員。由此亦可發現到，Sony Pictures 隨着帶來《Venom》，開始進入 Spider-Man 的漫畫世界，而《Venom》的成功將會促成 Sony 計劃製作一系列續集和獨立電影，《Sinister Six》可能便會是其中一部。但為了建立這個特許經營權，Sony 便需要一個名稱如 Marvel 的 MCU（Marvel Cinematic Universe）和 DC 的 DCEU（DC Extended Universe）。而在昨日 Variety 的一篇文章中提到，原來 Sony 已經正式命名自家 Marvel 電影宇宙觀為 SUMC（Sony&rsquo;s Universe of Marvel Characters），這命名看來十分有意義，因為 Spider-Man 其實連接了很多角色，除了他外其實還有 900 個潛在角色可供使用。而若果 Sony 僅只考慮 Spider-Man 的情況下命名特許經營權將會有所限制，所以 SUMC 相對自由度大一些。<br />\n<br />\nSpider-Man connects to a lot of the characters. There are villains, heroes, and antiheroes, and a lot are female characters, many of whom are bona fide, fully dimensionalised, and utterly unique.<br />\n同時 Sony 已經確認開拍《Morbius: The Living Vampire》，由 Jared Leto 負責飾演。同時還有《Kraven the Hunter》的劇本正在構思中，這樣更可延伸出更多不同角色如 Silk，Jackpot， Black Cat，Silver Sable 及 Nightwatch，希望藉此讓 Sony Pictures 可以有機會描繪更多樣化的角色。那麼各位又會希望 Sony Pictures 在《Venom》之後帶來甚麼和 Spider-Man 的故事呢？不妨在留言中互相討論，同時繼續留意我們 HYPEBEAST 有關的報導。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/8/sony-marvel-movie-universe-now-has-an-official-name?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=facebook_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2018%2F8%2Fsony-marvel-movie-universe-now-has-an-official-name%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dfacebook_post&d=nHpEuDdXp%2FE%2BTSxY8EHLBaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=789688e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/8/sony-marvel-movie-universe-now-has-an-official-name?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=facebook_post</a><br />\n<br />\n咁撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e85c27dd0e4612496df707c25b65cc41b3430d","tid":778423,"uid":64922,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T17:55:18.000Z","msg":"sony咁做岩時機啦！<br />\n出個豬豬俠宇宙<br />\n等下年同marvel合拍豬豬俠滿約有更高談判能力，<br />\nsony出佢自己豬豬俠時應要有更大自由度，<br />\n唔得咪同marvel拉倒拍返sony豬豬俠宇宙好過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3400a0b27cfd931e7dce1c326d3447a007dbaef4","tid":778423,"uid":92690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T18:41:45.000Z","msg":"自家真係無興趣睇，以前都試過兩次啦"},{"pid":"ba900e89fb2d8c3ab09bf4b8f29d90cff27f3377","tid":778423,"uid":126699,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T21:06:23.000Z","msg":"Venom冇同MCU connect都已經唔太想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n堆乜撚vampire真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3baef5b0ae52106e78bde1c28b635b0194cbcd87","tid":778423,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T21:58:12.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47980a9203189049e2af9f5680bb1f4679a0c3a6","tid":778423,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:40:50.000Z","msg":"其實係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b657f52979c359fba8bf51ee6ddaa14f8eb037","tid":778423,"uid":63913,"like":1,"dislike":10,"sc